# Uploading to Stores

After building, you can submit your app directly to App Store Connect and Google Play Console using EAS Submit.

Configure submission in `eas.json` under the `submit` key:

```json
{
  "submit": {
    "production": {
      "ios": {
        "appleId": "your@apple.id",
        "ascAppId": "1234567890"
      },
      "android": {
        "serviceAccountKeyPath": "./path/to/key.json"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Then run:
```bash
eas submit -p ios --profile production
```

You'll need to have your store listings created first (app name, description, screenshots).
